title: Bonus Episode: Jack Harlow Talks New Album + Drake and Jack Harlow Leak
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Jack Harlow sits down with Ebro in the Morning for a great conversation about his journey, new album, and some of his opportunities outside of music.

Harlow also discusses his success and being compared to the likes of Eminem, his hair, being in the industry and not drinking or smoking, working with the likes of EST Gee, Drake, and Kanye West. going into acting with a reboot of 'White Men Can't Jump' and more! His new album 'Come Home The Kids Miss You' is available this Friday, 5/6.
